radiographic_examinations.findings: Bibasilar dependent atelectasis, multiple hepatic lesions including a 1.6 cm simple cyst in hepatic segment VI, fluid-filled and abnormally dilated appendix measuring up to 1.1 cm with mucosal hyperenhancement and periappendiceal fat stranding, small amount of free fluid in the pelvis, a 1.9 cm cyst in the left ovary, no evidence of perforation or adjacent abscess formation.
